{"words":[{"word":"elegance","count":7},{"word":"students","count":5},{"word":"must","count":4},{"word":"dueling","count":3},{"word":"club","count":3},{"word":"professor","count":3},{"word":"style","count":2},{"word":"elegant","count":2},{"word":"advisor","count":2},{"word":"maintain","count":2},{"word":"respect","count":2},{"word":"another","count":2},{"word":"defeat","count":2},{"word":"skills","count":2},{"word":"lost","count":1},{"word":"stood","count":1},{"word":"defeated","count":1},{"word":"normal","count":1},{"word":"possessed","count":1},{"word":"form","count":1},{"word":"sense","count":1},{"word":"triumphed","count":1},{"word":"grass","count":1},{"word":"green","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"etiquette","count":1},{"word":"discipline","count":1},{"word":"order","count":1},{"word":"disciplined","count":1},{"word":"campus","count":1},{"word":"professors","count":1},{"word":"shining","count":1},{"word":"beacons","count":1},{"word":"ideal","count":1},{"word":"activities","count":1},{"word":"ought","count":1},{"word":"require","count":1},{"word":"professor's","count":1},{"word":"guiding","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"lest","count":1},{"word":"descend","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"utter","count":1},{"word":"anarchy","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"graced","count":1},{"word":"mind","count":1},{"word":"sufficiently","count":1},{"word":"affable","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"relations","count":1},{"word":"fan","count":1},{"word":"disciplinarian","count":1},{"word":"aura","count":1},{"word":"unyielding","count":1},{"word":"authority","count":1},{"word":"rejected","count":1},{"word":"idea","count":1},{"word":"besides","count":1},{"word":"exactly","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"person","count":1},{"word":"deduct","count":1},{"word":"points","count":1},{"word":"according","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"guidelines","count":1},{"word":"without","count":1},{"word":"problem","count":1},{"word":"beyond","count":1},{"word":"struggle","count":1},{"word":"interact","count":1},{"word":"aware","count":1},{"word":"regard","count":1},{"word":"abject","count":1},{"word":"terror","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"close","count":1},{"word":"fondness","count":1},{"word":"indeed","count":1},{"word":"mr","count":1},{"word":"furius","count":1},{"word":"mentioned","count":1},{"word":"lecture","count":1},{"word":"sometimes","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"effective","count":1},{"word":"words","count":1},{"word":"fellow","count":1},{"word":"duelists","count":1},{"word":"tend","count":1},{"word":"resonate","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"instead","count":1},{"word":"merely","count":1},{"word":"fear","count":1},{"word":"lead","count":1},{"word":"everyone","count":1},{"word":"cannot","count":1},{"word":"afford","count":1},{"word":"today","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"future","count":1},{"word":"members","count":1},{"word":"weep","count":1},{"word":"beauty","count":1},{"word":"continue","count":1},{"word":"refine","count":1},{"word":"per","count":1},{"word":"rules","count":1},{"word":"festa","count":1},{"word":"final","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"calith","count":1},{"word":"proven","count":1},{"word":"terrifying","count":1},{"word":"duelist","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"spreadsheet","count":1},{"word":"precision","count":1},{"word":"deadly","count":1},{"word":"machine","count":1},{"word":"guard","count":1},{"word":"playername","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"I have lost. The elegance I stood by... was defeated?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"No... this is normal. After all, your dueling style possessed its own form of elegance. In a sense, elegance still triumphed...!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Is the grass green? Of course it is! Elegance is etiquette. Elegance is discipline. Elegance is order.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Students must be disciplined and elegant while on campus. And we professors should be shining beacons of that ideal.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Even club activities ought to require a professor's guiding hand, lest they descend into utter anarchy!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"The thought has graced my mind. But an advisor must be sufficiently affable to maintain good relations with students in the fan club.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"But I am a disciplinarian! I must maintain an aura of unyielding authority! So I rejected such an idea.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Besides, I'm... not exactly a people person. I can deduct points according to Academy guidelines without problem, but beyond that, I struggle to interact with the students.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I'm aware the students regard me more with \"abject terror\" than anything close to fondness or respect.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...Indeed. Mr. Furius mentioned in his lecture that dueling can sometimes be far more effective than words.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Fellow duelists tend to resonate with one another... Perhaps you're right. Instead of being a professor whom students merely fear, I could be one... whom they respect.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"But if I am to lead everyone, I cannot afford another defeat such as today.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"To become an advisor with skills so elegant that future club members weep at its beauty, I must continue to refine my dueling skills.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"As per the rules, you still need to defeat Professor Festa before your final match with Professor Calith.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"She has proven to be a terrifying duelist. Though her style may have all the elegance of a spreadsheet, her precision is as deadly as a machine.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Be on your guard, {PlayerName}.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019}]}